headline: AI and online travel: Disruption or reinvention?
summary: Investing.com -- Artificial intelligence is changing the travel booking landscape, and Bernstein Research says the shift could redefine how online travel agencies operate, with Booking Holdings, Airbnb, and Expedia standing at the center of the transformation.
